nodes.text: Oven-roasted Burra Fish was a dish served at Docking Bay 7 Food and Cargo at Black Spire Outpost on the planet Batuu in around 34 ABY. The dish consisted of oven-roasted Burra fish served with vegetables, seeds and a sauce. It was suitable for consumption by humans.

Oven-roasted Burra Fish is a meal that is available for purchase by guests from the Docking Bay 7 Food and Cargo food stand at Star Wars: Galaxy's Edge upon its opening in 2019. The dish consists of a Dijon-crusted sustainable fish with mixed greens, roasted vegetables, quinoa and pumpkin seeds with a creamy green curry ranch dressing.
